        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I ran into the same doc generation issue when building for WASM. The fix I found was adding a `NVIM_HOST_PRG` variable to `runtime/CMakeLists.txt` when cross-compiling, it uses a host native nvim binary instead of the cross-compiled target binary. This should work for Android builds as well. I will open a PR for this.",
